{"tid":2307732,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"互聯網同埋智能手機之後既 “Next Big Thing”","createTime":"2020-12-01T10:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T00:53:24.000Z","uid":263434,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"05071fc93be9bd171261efd9428a62ccccb2476c","tid":2307732,"uid":263434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:59:55.000Z","msg":"The Next Big Thing好有機會係人機接口 Brain-computer Interface (BCI), 即係好似Neuralink 咁。 <br />\n不過顧及成本同埋便利程度，非入侵式嘅BCI 有更大機會成為主流。<br />\n而非入侵式BCI 可以用 EEG 或 fMRI 訊號。<br />\nfMRI訊號 非入侵式BCI 比EEG更有可能突圍而出，因為EEG 有更多noise 同埋fMRI 跟據大腦嘅3D structure (不同思考區域），有更大機會成功將訊號interpret 成一個 &ldquo;thought&rdquo; 或者一個完整句子。<br />\n而如果fMRI Scanner 可以做到便攜式，呢種BCI 就更有機會製成。<br />\n<br />\n不過要成功研發，除咗要好多錢亦要好多data。<br />\n估計都係要美國醫院同埋科技巨頭頂尖neurologist, data scientist, electronic engineer 合作先得。<br />\n一個普通人去startup event pitch 啲人只會當你癡線。"},{"pid":"c64c2c39c1df9562c119432ebcc4932ade5f1307","tid":2307732,"uid":148652,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T16:05:27.000Z","msg":"IOT呢？AI呢？ 講左10世都好似仲未流行既"},{"pid":"6cf1781d22db59158216f5cc0a8d0810b2946539","tid":2307732,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T16:10:31.000Z","msg":"整左SAO先啦"},{"pid":"b19695640742074924f259ea15fd28733a74a7b9","tid":2307732,"uid":148652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T16:20:08.000Z","msg":"仲有個5G呢, 現場同理想差好遠下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c486a11db49c5427a2f77a6e6cb63192e0b28a1e","tid":2307732,"uid":253234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T16:21:31.000Z","msg":"人類對neuro science 都認識唔多<br />\n好多野都未搵到mechanism<br />\n真係可以做到人機融合咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3196138559cbd24f91be1e476e3ff95de28a2d5","tid":2307732,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T00:38:23.000Z","msg":"有得玩完全潛行遊戲先講啦仆街"},{"pid":"f6f09941